      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2496688/" class="title-link">这本书的中心思想</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2496688"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1864500/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1864500-30.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1864500/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">锅巴</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-10-11"
      class="main-meta">2009-10-11 14:33:28</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2496688_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  重读《道德理想国的覆灭》，这本书的关键词是“政治神学论”、“越界”。  朱学勤认为，政治神学论是中世纪“神学政治论”的变相延伸。放弃了神学形式，但是没有放弃神学的理想，把这一理想从天上移到了凡间。要在人间实现天堂理想。本来，上帝的鬼上帝，凯撒的归凯撒，现在，...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2496688/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2496688_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2496688_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










